{"tid":1851491,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何栢良倡警找出湖北旅客　林志偉：不反對，但應有醫護隨行","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:06:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":56,"dislike":378,"uniUserReply":178,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bdd9478270156fe4b219c70101f2081412e4be","tid":1851491,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良建議政府應派警員巡查酒店，強行隔離或送走來自湖北的旅客。警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉回覆稱，不反對有關建議，行動應有醫護人員隨行。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉回覆《南華早報》查詢時指，不反對有關建議，但指工作牽涉醫護界專業知識，為說服目標人士配合，行動應有醫護人員隨行，向需被隔離人士解釋及即時檢查。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，如果有法例賦予警員必要時，需強制具隔離必要的人配合政府指示，亦會依法積極配合，作為專業紀律部隊成員，不會抗拒。"},{"pid":"78214ff32f544dc6df34cbd0fbd98002f98989d7","tid":1851491,"uid":122275,"like":185,"dislike":2,"score":183,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:09:21.000Z","msg":"澳門洗唔洗醫護啊<br />\n垃撚圾"},{"pid":"880a6e7efeb584a79acea9e84a3f02b681d4d902","tid":1851491,"uid":328405,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:10:04.000Z","msg":"驚死？"},{"pid":"393b577e298f4061b9c0859ae83ec5d15ae952c2","tid":1851491,"uid":249263,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=7a3d7531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHel